summary:
Alexander is a published entrepreneurial Senior Leader with a B.Sc. in UX and M.Sc. in Computer Science. He has a strong track record in technology innovation, people leadership, building, leading and managing large departments. He is recognised as an inspirational leader and driver of excellence and innovation leading to company growth.

Alexander has been focussed on engineering/technology/product development leadership with nearly 18+ years of experience in fintech, eCommerce and enterprise scale SaaS solutions. He is a customer centric, pragmatic, outcome driven professional through lean delivery delivering on expectations, budget, security parameters and engineering quality.

Alexander understands the business, product, and technology needs and knows how to connect these to get the focus needed to achieve measured customer outcomes resulting in revenue growth.

Competencies:
- Driving customer experience;
- Outcome over Output;
- Engineering craftsmanship;
- Delivery, deployment, digital strategy and architecture;
- Inspiring professional, but down to earth “get things done” fun pragmatic person;
- (High traffic) environments, conversion optimisation, usability and customer journey, A/B testing, content management;
- Defining and prioritising strategy;
- Experienced working in larger scale Agile, Waterfall or Hybrid environments;
- SEO, SEA, e-mail marketing, social media, affiliates, display, retargeting, brand management;
- CRM, creating customer satisfaction and customer lock-in;
- Analytics and Big Data environment;
- Collaborating and communicating with cross functional teams i.e. marketing, product, IT, logistics;
- Inspirational people manager, excellent leadership skills, team builder;
- Attracting and retaining skilled people
- Building and managing (Agile) delivery teams within a scaling software architecture for high-traffic services.

